in the directors page, to get info about an employee and all of them use the same form.
if the empId we search is entered  we disable the other fields, else we search based on the other fields and 
return a json list of employees tha fulfill the criteria.

regarding employees in Directors Page.

1)new Employee (all emp data except emp id): (ret nothing)
2)employeeInfo (empId || the rest of empData {json_String}) : (JSON{LIST<Employee>})
3)alterEmployee 2 phase.  a) get employee info & select employee , b) alter employee data & save   

4) getTransactions(date1,date2): JSON{list<transactions>}
5) getBalance (date1, date2): JSON{ List<day,trDate,withdraw,deposit>}



